title: 2007 Nissan Sentra Factory Service Manual
description:
2007 specific but also works for 2008
Nissan Sentra, all models

Very detailed mechanical information including the central computer, wiring, fuses, and anything else you can think of. The searchable PDFs are named by 3 letter abbreviations which is annoying but I didn&#039;t feel like changing them all. ex CVT=continuously variable transmission.

Professional Factory Service Manuals that can be used to repair, service, and maintain your vehicles.

This manual contains info on what is listed below and much more.
